    • Method Detail

      • buy

        AssociatedNumber buy()
              throws ForbiddenAccessException,
                     BadRequestException,
                     UnauthorizedAccessException,
                     ServerErrorException,
                     ApiRequestException
        Buys this number and adds it to your account.

        Take a look at the "See also" section to see which optional properties can be set prior to purchasing this number.

        For more details on how to purchase a number, please refer to the VivialConnect "How to Purchase a Number" API guide.

        Returns:
        the newly-purchased number, associated to your account
        Throws:
        ForbiddenAccessException - if the user does not have permission to the API resource
        BadRequestException - if the request params and/or payload are not valid
        UnauthorizedAccessException - if any of the auth properties account ID, API Key and/or API secret are not valid
        ServerErrorException - if the server is unable to process the request
        ApiRequestException - if an API error occurs
        See Also:
        INumber.setName(java.lang.String), INumber.setStatusTextUrl(java.lang.String), INumber.setConnectorId(int), INumber.setIncomingTextUrl(java.lang.String), INumber.setIncomingTextMethod(net.vivialconnect.model.enums.CallbackMethod), INumber.setIncomingTextFallbackUrl(java.lang.String), INumber.setIncomingTextFallbackMethod(net.vivialconnect.model.enums.CallbackMethod)
